CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 9, 2013

[Cite as 05/0912013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-1886.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2005-2250. Disciplinary Counsel v. Giba.

This cause came on for further consideration upon respondent’s filing of a motion to purge contempt. Upon consideration thereof, this court orders that the motion is granted.
